00:01:21.950 --> 00:01:27.530
The DMS is an FDA-approved medical device.
The mechanism of action of Deep Muscle Stimulation

00:01:27.530 --> 00:01:32.960
Massage involves providing deep muscle tissue
with kinetic forms of percussion and concussion

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:38.070
