RPM.

00:01:38.070 --> 00:01:42.570
Clients may remain fully clothed for these
sessions, as the vibration need not be applied

00:01:42.570 --> 00:01:47.520
directly to the skin. But we have found it
to be most effective when used in combination

00:01:47.520 --> 00:01:48.560
