00:01:48.560 --> 00:01:54.759
DMS Massage is extremely effective in targeting
and dissolving adhesions and trigger points

00:01:54.759 --> 00:01:59.530
and relieving pain relatively quickly and
comfortably. DMS Massage is most frequently

00:01:59.530 --> 00:02:02.369
focused on one or more trouble spots, rather
than on the entire body.

